    "title": "Hiring Store Manager at Om Book Shop Capital India",
    "description": "If you're a passionate Store Manager with drive and ambition, Om Book Shop Capital India in Ahmedabad is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout Om Book Shop Capital India:\nOm Book Shop Capital India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage store operations to ensure smooth daily functioning\n• Conduct regular stock audits and prevent pilferage\n• Coordinate with the supply chain team for timely stock delivery\n• Achieve sales targets and improve store performance metrics\n• Ensure visual merchandising standards are maintained at all times\n• Manage shrinkage and reduce stock discrepancies\n• Build relationships with regular customers to drive loyalty\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Com / M.Com / MBA Finance\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Retail Operations\n• Proficiency in Sales Techniques\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in Loyalty Programs\n• Proficiency in Visual Merchandising\n• Proficiency in Planogram\n• Proficiency in Category Management\n• Proficiency in POS Systems\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Referral bonus program\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ahmedabad, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Om Book Shop Capital India!",
